reviewText:
If you like to watch Soumitra (like me), then you might like it.

Otherwise, the plot and movie can't really stand itself.

Angshumaner Chobi bagged the Aravindan Award for Best Debut Director, 2010 and Kerala State  Award, Best Debut Film 2010 and has a credited star cast of Indraneil Sengupta, Tota Roy Chowdhury, Soumitra Chatterjee, Indrani halder, Rudraneil Ghosh, Ananya Chatterjee, Sabyasachi Chakraborty, Bhaskar Banerjee and others.
